<Para>The CDL penalty for a missing door is zero and the above procedure does not apply when operating with the landing gear extended (Appendix 1) for the entire flight.</Para>
</Note>
<Para>For 787-9, increase flight planning fuel by 2,900 pounds (1,315 kg) for landing gear extended for 10 minutes.</Para>
<Para>For 787-10, increase flight planning fuel by 2,800 pounds (1,270 kg) for landing gear extended for 10 minutes.</Para>
